      items={[
        { stat: "Pellets", label: "The Base", body: "A formulated, color-free pellet is the foundation (60–80% of the diet) — never an all-seed mix, which causes vitamin-A and calcium deficiency." },
        { stat: "#1", label: "Harrison's", body: "Certified organic and the pellet most avian vets reach for — our top all-round pick for a Grey, especially birds coming off seed." },
        { stat: "Natural", label: "Zupreem / Roudybush", body: "Zupreem Natural (the dye-free line) and Roudybush are excellent, easier-to-find, budget-friendlier complete pellets." },
